messages.text: Lufthansa Group Inspirational AI flight assistant. Nice to meet you!
Hello! To start planning your journey, could you please share your travel intentions? Are you looking for a one-way or round trip, and any specific dates or destinations in mind?
I want to go to Zurich next saturday. Stay for seven days. Only me.
Thank you for sharing your plans. To proceed, could you please confirm the departure date for next Saturday and let me know from which airport you will be departing?
25th of October, the nearest airport to my location.
Thank you for the details. To find the best flights, could you please provide the name of the nearest airport to your location?
I'm here to assist you with your travel plans. To find the best flights to Zurich, could you please provide the name of the nearest airport to your location?
